import currentDate from 'app/utils/helpers';

export const Vendor = {
	id: null,
	name: '',
	locality: '',
	logo: '',
	pw: '',
	qrc: '',
	has_pos: 0,
	latitude: '',
	longitude: '',
	email: '',
	pin: '',
	status: 'inactive',
	pingable: 0,
	mkt: 0,
	featured_social: 0,
	featured_website: 0,
	livedt: currentDate(),
	mupd_id: '',
	description: '',
	phone: '',
	header: '',
	address: '',
	promo_pts: 300,
	redeemed: 0,
	partners: [{ id: 1, name: 'vouch365' }],
	memberships: [],
	city: {},
	amenities: [],
	category: {},
	is_live: 0,
	is_live_retail: 0,
	is_live_corporate: 0,
	is_completed: 0,
	dinein: 0,
	takeaway: 0,
	delivery: 0
};
